1
00:06:51,903 --> 00:06:55,124
<font color="#ffff00">The food is terrible.
Worst shit I've ever seen, man.</font>

2
00:06:56,908 --> 00:06:59,368
<font color="#ffff00">What you say?
You got any biscuits over there?</font>

3
00:06:59,452 --> 00:07:01,787
<font color="#ffff00">I keep seeing corn bread.</font>

4
00:07:04,241 --> 00:07:07,301
<font color="#ffff00">- I am cold.
- Still with us, Brett?</font>

5
00:07:07,685 --> 00:07:08,963
<font color="#ffff00">Right.</font>

6
00:07:09,387 --> 00:07:11,487
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, I feel dead.</font>

7
00:07:11,548 --> 00:07:14,225
<font color="#ffff00">Anybody ever tell you
you look dead, man?</font>

8
00:07:17,045 --> 00:07:19,346
<font color="#ffff00">Oh, yeah, right.</font>

9
00:07:19,431 --> 00:07:21,515
<font color="#ffff00">Now, I just
forgot something, man.</font>

10
00:07:21,599 --> 00:07:23,559
<font color="#ffff00">Before we dock,</font>

11
00:07:23,643 --> 00:07:25,644
<font color="#ffff00">I think we oughta discuss
the bonus situation.</font>

12
00:07:25,770 --> 00:07:27,771
<font color="#ffff00">Right.
Brett and I, we think we oughta-</font>

13
00:07:27,856 --> 00:07:30,232
<font color="#ffff00">- we deserve full shares, right, baby?
- You see, Mr. Parker and I...</font>

14
00:07:30,317 --> 00:07:33,944
<font color="#ffff00">feel that the bonus situation
has never been on an equitable level.</font>

15
00:07:34,029 --> 00:07:37,281
<font color="#ffff00">Well, you'll get what you're
contracted for like everybody else.</font>

16
00:07:37,407 --> 00:07:39,742
<font color="#ffff00">Yes, but everybody else
gets more than us.</font>

17
00:07:39,826 --> 00:07:41,994
<font color="#ffff00">Dallas, Mother
wants to talk to you.</font>

18
00:07:42,078 --> 00:07:45,497
<font color="#ffff00">Huh? Yeah, I saw it.
Yellow light's for my eyes only.</font>

19
00:07:46,916 --> 00:07:48,667
<font color="#ffff00">OK, get dressed, huh?</font>

20
00:07:48,793 --> 00:07:52,212
<font color="#ffff00">Parker, come on.
Can I finish my coffee? Thank you.</font>

21
00:07:52,297 --> 00:07:54,357
<font color="#ffff00">It's the only thing
good on this ship.</font>

22
00:08:41,988 --> 00:08:44,198
<font color="#ffff00">Morning, Mother.</font>

23
00:09:14,170 --> 00:09:16,281
<font color="#ffff00">- Right.
- OK.</font>

24
00:09:17,465 --> 00:09:19,200
<font color="#ffff00">Plug us in.</font>

25
00:09:21,010 --> 00:09:22,470
<font color="#ffff00">Thank you.</font>

26
00:09:26,391 --> 00:09:28,026
<font color="#ffff00">Where's Earth?</font>

27
00:09:28,250 --> 00:09:30,150
<font color="#ffff00">You should know.</font>

28
00:09:30,211 --> 00:09:32,280
<font color="#ffff00">It's not our system.</font>

29
00:09:33,064 --> 00:09:34,305
<font color="#ffff00">Scan.</font>

30
00:09:37,026 --> 00:09:39,428
<font color="#ffff00">I can't believe this.</font>

31
00:09:40,113 --> 00:09:42,565
<font color="#ffff00">Contact Traffic Control.</font>

32
00:09:43,449 --> 00:09:47,828
<font color="#ffff00"><i>This is commercial towing vehicle
Nostromo out of the Solomons.</i></font>

33
00:09:47,912 --> 00:09:51,957
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Registration number:
1-8-0-niner-2-4-6-0-niner.</i></font>

34
00:09:52,041 --> 00:09:56,328
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Calling Antarctica Traffic Control.
Can you read me? Over.</i></font>

35
00:09:56,713 --> 00:09:59,965
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Commercial towing vehicle
Nostromo out of the Solomons,</i></font>

36
00:10:00,049 --> 00:10:02,050
<font color="#ffff00"><i>registration number...</i></font>

37
00:10:06,198 --> 00:10:08,499
<font color="#ffff00">- Nothing.
- Keep trying.</font>

38
00:10:08,523 --> 00:10:12,951
<font color="#ffff00">Calling Antarctica Traffic Control.
Do you read me, Antarctica? Over.</font>

39
00:10:13,738 --> 00:10:17,741
<font color="#ffff00">I found it.
Just short of Zeta II Reticuli.</font>

40
00:10:17,767 --> 00:10:20,130
<font color="#ffff00">We haven't reached
the outer rim yet.</font>

41
00:10:20,254 --> 00:10:22,254
<font color="#ffff00">That's hard to believe.</font>

42
00:10:23,315 --> 00:10:25,759
<font color="#ffff00">What the hell are we doing out here?</font>

43
00:10:27,044 --> 00:10:28,495
<font color="#ffff00">I don't know.</font>

44
00:10:28,619 --> 00:10:30,656
<font color="#ffff00">What the hell are you talking about?</font>

45
00:10:30,680 --> 00:10:33,957
<font color="#ffff00">- That's not our system.
- I know that.</font>

46
00:10:34,283 --> 00:10:37,570
<font color="#ffff00">Do you ever notice
how they never come down here?</font>

47
00:10:38,254 --> 00:10:40,380
<font color="#ffff00">I mean, this is where
the work is, right?</font>

48
00:10:40,465 --> 00:10:43,133
<font color="#ffff00">Well, it's the same damn reason
we get a half share to their one.</font>

49
00:10:43,218 --> 00:10:45,260
<font color="#ffff00">Our time is their time.
That's the way they see it.</font>

50
00:10:45,386 --> 00:10:47,304
<font color="#ffff00">- No, but...
- Same old shit, man.</font>

51
00:10:47,388 --> 00:10:49,514
<font color="#ffff00">I think I know why they
don't come down here.</font>

52
00:10:49,599 --> 00:10:52,100
<font color="#ffff00">It's because of you.
You don't have the personality.</font>

53
00:10:54,103 --> 00:10:56,997
<font color="#ffff00">Wonder what they want now.
What's going on down here?</font>

54
00:10:59,567 --> 00:11:02,753
<font color="#ffff00">- Um, you happen to be in my seat.
Can I have it? - Yes, of course.</font>

55
00:11:02,779 --> 00:11:04,997
<font color="#ffff00">- Thank you.
- I'm sorry.</font>

56
00:11:10,286 --> 00:11:12,287
<font color="#ffff00">What's happenin' now, baby?</font>

57
00:11:14,123 --> 00:11:15,535
<font color="#ffff00">Well,</font>

58
00:11:15,759 --> 00:11:18,359
<font color="#ffff00">some of you may have
figured out we're not home yet.</font>

59
00:11:18,419 --> 00:11:20,796
<font color="#ffff00">- We're only halfway there.
- What?</font>

60
00:11:20,880 --> 00:11:24,058
<font color="#ffff00">Mother's interrupted
the course of our journey.</font>

61
00:11:24,342 --> 00:11:25,860
<font color="#ffff00">- Why?
- Yeah.</font>

62
00:11:25,884 --> 00:11:29,428
<font color="#ffff00">She's programmed to do that should
certain conditions arise. They have.</font>

63
00:11:29,514 --> 00:11:32,216
<font color="#ffff00">- Like what?
- It seems she has...</font>

64
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:34,810
<font color="#ffff00">intercepted a transmission
of unknown origin.</font>

65
00:11:34,936 --> 00:11:38,146
<font color="#ffff00">- She got us up to check it out.
- A transmission? Out here?</font>

66
00:11:38,231 --> 00:11:40,983
<font color="#ffff00">- Yeah.
- What kind of a transmission?</font>

67
00:11:41,067 --> 00:11:44,695
<font color="#ffff00">Acoustical beacon.
It repeats at intervals of 12 seconds.</font>

68
00:11:44,821 --> 00:11:46,697
<font color="#ffff00">- S.O.S.?
- I don't know.</font>

69
00:11:46,781 --> 00:11:48,299
<font color="#ffff00">Human?</font>

70
00:11:48,825 --> 00:11:51,660
<font color="#ffff00">- Unknown.
- Well, so what?</font>

71
00:11:51,744 --> 00:11:53,870
<font color="#ffff00">We are obligated under section eight...</font>

72
00:11:53,955 --> 00:11:56,248
<font color="#ffff00">I hate to bring this up, but, uh,</font>

73
00:11:56,332 --> 00:11:58,767
<font color="#ffff00">this is a commercial ship,
not a rescue ship.</font>

74
00:11:58,793 --> 00:12:02,212
<font color="#ffff00">- Right. - And it's not in my contract
to do this kind of duty.</font>

75
00:12:02,338 --> 00:12:06,316
<font color="#ffff00">And what about the money?
If you wanna give me some money,
I'll be happy to oblige.</font>

76
00:12:06,342 --> 00:12:08,635
<font color="#ffff00">- The man's right.
- Let's go over the bonus situation.</font>

77
00:12:08,720 --> 00:12:12,639
<font color="#ffff00">- I'm sorry. Can I say something?
- Let's talk about the bonus more.</font>

78
00:12:12,724 --> 00:12:15,350
<font color="#ffff00">There is a clause in the contract
which specifically states...</font>

79
00:12:15,435 --> 00:12:18,603
<font color="#ffff00">any systematised transmission indicating
a possible intelligent origin...</font>

80
00:12:18,730 --> 00:12:20,455
<font color="#ffff00">- must be investigated.
- I don't wanna hear it.</font>

81
00:12:20,481 --> 00:12:22,649
<font color="#ffff00">We don't know if it's intelligent.
I wanna go home and party.</font>

82
00:12:22,734 --> 00:12:25,027
<font color="#ffff00">Parker, will you
just listen to the man?</font>

83
00:12:27,238 --> 00:12:30,442
<font color="#ffff00">On penalty of total forfeiture
of shares.</font>

84
00:12:30,466 --> 00:12:32,166
<font color="#ffff00">No money.</font>

85
00:12:33,119 --> 00:12:34,703
<font color="#ffff00">You got that?</font>

86
00:12:34,787 --> 00:12:38,540
<font color="#ffff00">- Well... yeah.
- All right, we're going in.</font>

87
00:12:38,624 --> 00:12:40,642
<font color="#ffff00">Yeah. We're goin' in, aren't we?</font>

88
00:12:47,550 --> 00:12:49,617
<font color="#ffff00">Can we all hear that, Lambert?</font>

89
00:13:12,033 --> 00:13:13,892
<font color="#ffff00">Good God.</font>

90
00:13:14,077 --> 00:13:16,553
<font color="#ffff00">Doesn't sound like
any radio signal I've heard.</font>

91
00:13:16,579 --> 00:13:18,747
<font color="#ffff00">- Maybe it's a voice.
- Well, we'll soon know.</font>

92
00:13:18,831 --> 00:13:20,916
<font color="#ffff00">Can you hone in on that?</font>

93
00:13:21,843 --> 00:13:24,453
<font color="#ffff00">What was the, uh, position?</font>

94
00:13:24,837 --> 00:13:28,632
<font color="#ffff00">6550-99.</font>

95
00:13:33,629 --> 00:13:36,306
<font color="#ffff00">All right.
It found the quadrant.</font>

96
00:13:36,391 --> 00:13:40,027
<font color="#ffff00">Ascension: 6 minutes, 20 seconds.</font>

97
00:13:40,111 --> 00:13:42,198
<font color="#ffff00">Declination:</font>

98
00:13:42,222 --> 00:13:44,822
<font color="#ffff00">39 degrees, 2 seconds.</font>

99
00:13:44,982 --> 00:13:47,150
<font color="#ffff00">OK. Put that on the screen for me.</font>

100
00:13:51,697 --> 00:13:53,532
<font color="#ffff00">All right. Well, that's it.</font>

101
00:13:53,616 --> 00:13:55,335
<font color="#ffff00">It's a planetoid.</font>

102
00:13:55,359 --> 00:13:57,096
<font color="#ffff00">1200 kilometres.</font>

103
00:13:57,120 --> 00:13:58,663
<font color="#ffff00">It's tiny.</font>

104
00:13:58,687 --> 00:14:00,687
<font color="#ffff00">Any rotation?</font>

105
00:14:02,125 --> 00:14:04,343
<font color="#ffff00">About two hours.</font>

106
00:14:04,527 --> 00:14:06,462
<font color="#ffff00">What about gravity?</font>

107
00:14:07,146 --> 00:14:09,423
<font color="#ffff00">Point eight-six.</font>

108
00:14:11,517 --> 00:14:13,544
<font color="#ffff00">You can walk on it.</font>

109
00:14:23,212 --> 00:14:26,040
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Approaching orbital apogee.</i></font>

110
00:14:26,924 --> 00:14:30,243
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Mark 12, 11...</i></font>

111
00:14:30,327 --> 00:14:32,346
<font color="#ffff00">Equatorial orbit nailed.</font>

112
00:14:32,430 --> 00:14:35,724
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Nine, eight seconds on descent.</i></font>

113
00:14:35,808 --> 00:14:38,977
<font color="#ffff00">- Grids energised. Fields focused.
- <i>Five. Four...</i></font>

114
00:14:47,445 --> 00:14:50,489
<font color="#ffff00">- D.O.R.'s on line.
- How's the status on the lifters?</font>

115
00:14:50,573 --> 00:14:53,016
<font color="#ffff00">Give me an A.C. pressure reading.</font>

116
00:14:59,624 --> 00:15:02,317
<font color="#ffff00">Forty-eight seconds and counting.</font>

117
00:15:02,502 --> 00:15:04,945
<font color="#ffff00"><i>SR-1 stable.</i></font>

118
00:15:05,129 --> 00:15:07,631
<font color="#ffff00">Prepare to disengage
from platform.</font>

119
00:15:07,715 --> 00:15:12,511
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Mark, 20 seconds.
Eighteen, 17-</i></font>

120
00:15:12,595 --> 00:15:16,890
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Twelve, 11, 10,</i></font>

121
00:15:16,974 --> 00:15:19,559
<font color="#ffff00"><i>nine, eight, seven...</i></font>

122
00:15:19,644 --> 00:15:23,355
<font color="#ffff00"><i>six, five, four,</i></font>

123
00:15:23,439 --> 00:15:27,100
<font color="#ffff00"><i>three, two, one, lock.</i></font>

124
00:15:27,284 --> 00:15:28,919
<font color="#ffff00">Disengage.</font>

125
00:15:33,950 --> 00:15:35,984
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Umbilicus clear.</i></font>

126
00:15:40,456 --> 00:15:43,408
<font color="#ffff00">Money's safe.
Let's take her down.</font>

127
00:15:45,670 --> 00:15:50,549
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Nine, eight, seven-</i></font>

128
00:15:50,633 --> 00:15:53,427
<font color="#ffff00">Roll 92 degrees port yaw.</font>

129
00:15:53,611 --> 00:15:55,429
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Prime to port.</i></font>

130
00:16:15,542 --> 00:16:17,177
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Prime ventral.</i></font>

131
00:16:17,401 --> 00:16:19,138
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Prime dorsal.</i></font>

132
00:16:19,162 --> 00:16:20,720
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Down a degree.</i></font>

133
00:16:25,376 --> 00:16:27,393
<font color="#ffff00">39,000 metres.</font>

134
00:16:34,051 --> 00:16:35,787
<font color="#ffff00">Turbulence.</font>

135
00:16:44,228 --> 00:16:47,480
<font color="#ffff00">Locked and floating. You can drop us
anytime now. We'll catch you.</font>

136
00:16:47,565 --> 00:16:51,802
<font color="#ffff00">Inertial damping's going off. Hold on,
people.There's gonna be a little bump.</font>

137
00:16:58,910 --> 00:17:01,128
<font color="#ffff00">What the hell was that?</font>

138
00:17:01,212 --> 00:17:03,872
<font color="#ffff00">Pressure drop in intake three.
Must've lost a shield.</font>

139
00:17:03,956 --> 00:17:05,607
<font color="#ffff00">Let's go with it.</font>

140
00:17:14,216 --> 00:17:16,416
<font color="#ffff00">Dropping off now.</font>

141
00:17:17,929 --> 00:17:19,630
<font color="#ffff00">Still dropping.</font>

142
00:17:21,641 --> 00:17:23,500
<font color="#ffff00">Here we are. We've got it.</font>

143
00:17:23,684 --> 00:17:25,719
<font color="#ffff00">Take her down.</font>

144
00:17:32,543 --> 00:17:34,669
<font color="#ffff00">Navigation lights on.</font>

145
00:17:42,161 --> 00:17:46,206
<font color="#ffff00">We've got 5-3 still out.
No problem. Just down 11%.</font>

146
00:17:46,290 --> 00:17:48,775
<font color="#ffff00">Grid status OK.</font>

147
00:18:08,079 --> 00:18:09,896
<font color="#ffff00">Nine,</font>

148
00:18:09,981 --> 00:18:13,400
<font color="#ffff00">eight, seven, six,</font>

149
00:18:13,484 --> 00:18:17,570
<font color="#ffff00">five, four, three,</font>

150
00:18:17,655 --> 00:18:19,572
<font color="#ffff00">two, one.</font>

151
00:18:19,657 --> 00:18:21,658
<font color="#ffff00">Kill drive engines.</font>

152
00:18:40,711 --> 00:18:42,729
<font color="#ffff00">What the hell happened?</font>

153
00:18:44,524 --> 00:18:47,124
<font color="#ffff00">Somebody give me a straight answer!</font>

154
00:18:47,184 --> 00:18:48,687
<font color="#ffff00">Is the hull breached?</font>

155
00:18:48,711 --> 00:18:51,211
<font color="#ffff00">I don't see anything.
We've still got pressure.</font>

156
00:18:51,272 --> 00:18:53,358
<font color="#ffff00">Hit the screen.</font>

157
00:18:53,882 --> 00:18:55,082
<font color="#ffff00">Right.</font>

158
00:19:02,266 --> 00:19:05,869
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Secondary load sharing unit...</i></font>

159
00:19:05,953 --> 00:19:07,871
<font color="#ffff00"><i>is out.</i></font>

160
00:19:07,955 --> 00:19:11,082
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Three to four cells are gone.</i></font>

161
00:19:13,544 --> 00:19:16,546
<font color="#ffff00">- Is that it?
- <i>No, hold on, uh...</i></font>

162
00:19:16,630 --> 00:19:19,924
<font color="#ffff00"><i>We can't fix it out here anyway,
and we need to reroute...</i></font>

163
00:19:20,051 --> 00:19:23,553
<font color="#ffff00">- <i>a couple of these ducts, wouldn't
you say, Brett?</i> - Dry dock time.</font>

164
00:19:23,637 --> 00:19:25,972
<font color="#ffff00">Dry dock.
Tell her we need to dry-dock.</font>

165
00:19:26,057 --> 00:19:27,974
<font color="#ffff00">Look, we couldn't fix it
out here anyway.</font>

166
00:19:28,059 --> 00:19:29,976
<font color="#ffff00">We gotta reroute
all these ducts,</font>

167
00:19:30,061 --> 00:19:32,687
<font color="#ffff00">and in order to do that
we've got to dry-dock.</font>

168
00:19:33,372 --> 00:19:35,023
<font color="#ffff00">What else?</font>

169
00:19:35,107 --> 00:19:37,025
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Some fragments kicked up and</i></font>

170
00:19:37,109 --> 00:19:39,486
<font color="#ffff00"><i>we've got to clean it all out
and repressurise it.</i></font>

171
00:19:39,570 --> 00:19:41,946
<font color="#ffff00"><i>How long before
we're functional?</i></font>

172
00:19:42,073 --> 00:19:45,693
<font color="#ffff00">- Look, what is... what...
- It's 17 hours, tell her.</font>

173
00:19:46,619 --> 00:19:49,412
<font color="#ffff00">- At least 25 hours.
- Yeah.</font>

174
00:19:49,497 --> 00:19:51,873
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Get started on the floor panel.
I'll be right down.</i></font>

175
00:19:51,957 --> 00:19:54,000
<font color="#ffff00">What the hell's she
comin' down here for?</font>

176
00:19:54,085 --> 00:19:56,169
<font color="#ffff00">She better stay the fuck out
of my way, I'll tell you that.</font>

177
00:19:56,253 --> 00:19:58,822
<font color="#ffff00">I'd like to see what she's
gonna do when she gets here.</font>

178
00:20:08,974 --> 00:20:12,585
<font color="#ffff00">- Any response yet?
- No. Absolutely nothing.</font>

179
00:20:12,770 --> 00:20:15,639
<font color="#ffff00">Except the same transmission
every 12 seconds.</font>

180
00:20:16,023 --> 00:20:18,024
<font color="#ffff00">All the other channels are dead.</font>

181
00:20:23,714 --> 00:20:26,116
<font color="#ffff00">Kick on the floods.</font>

182
00:20:40,798 --> 00:20:44,034
<font color="#ffff00">- We can't go anywhere in this.
- Mm.</font>

183
00:20:44,718 --> 00:20:47,011
<font color="#ffff00">Well, Mother says the sun's
coming up in 20 minutes.</font>

184
00:20:47,138 --> 00:20:50,473
<font color="#ffff00">- How far are we from the source
of transmission? - Uh, northeast.</font>

185
00:20:50,558 --> 00:20:52,976
<font color="#ffff00">Just under 2,000 metres.</font>

186
00:20:53,060 --> 00:20:54,862
<font color="#ffff00">Walking distance?</font>

187
00:20:55,646 --> 00:20:57,289
<font color="#ffff00">Well...</font>

188
00:20:58,315 --> 00:21:01,143
<font color="#ffff00">- Can you give me an atmospheric?
- Yes.</font>

189
00:21:04,488 --> 00:21:05,689
<font color="#ffff00">Oh.</font>

190
00:21:07,825 --> 00:21:09,909
<font color="#ffff00">It's almost primordial.</font>

191
00:21:09,994 --> 00:21:11,995
<font color="#ffff00">There's inert nitrogen,</font>

192
00:21:12,079 --> 00:21:14,747
<font color="#ffff00">high concentration of
carbon dioxide crystals, methane.</font>

193
00:21:14,832 --> 00:21:16,749
<font color="#ffff00">I'm working on the trace elements.</font>

194
00:21:16,834 --> 00:21:18,460
<font color="#ffff00">Anything else?</font>

195
00:21:18,544 --> 00:21:20,562
<font color="#ffff00">Yes. It's...</font>

196
00:21:20,586 --> 00:21:22,963
<font color="#ffff00">rock, lava base,</font>

197
00:21:23,507 --> 00:21:25,625
<font color="#ffff00">and... deep cold.</font>

198
00:21:25,709 --> 00:21:28,529
<font color="#ffff00">- Well below the line.
- Mm-hm.</font>

199
00:21:29,513 --> 00:21:32,182
<font color="#ffff00">I'll volunteer to be in
the first group to go out.</font>

200
00:21:32,266 --> 00:21:34,318
<font color="#ffff00">Yeah, that figures.</font>

201
00:21:35,102 --> 00:21:37,196
<font color="#ffff00">You too, Lambert.</font>

202
00:21:38,022 --> 00:21:39,224
<font color="#ffff00">Swell.</font>

203
00:21:39,248 --> 00:21:41,448
<font color="#ffff00">Better break out the weapons.</font>

204
00:22:55,449 --> 00:22:58,518
<font color="#ffff00">I can't see a god damn thing.</font>

205
00:23:00,020 --> 00:23:02,121
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Ash, are you receiving?</i></font>

206
00:23:06,819 --> 00:23:09,012
<font color="#ffff00">Good contact on my board.</font>

207
00:23:09,196 --> 00:23:12,049
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Clear and free.
Keep the line open.</i></font>

208
00:23:12,173 --> 00:23:13,473
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Let's go.</i></font>

209
00:23:27,798 --> 00:23:29,433
<font color="#ffff00">Hey, Ripley.</font>

210
00:23:30,718 --> 00:23:33,202
<font color="#ffff00">Hey, Ripley,
I wanna ask you a question.</font>

211
00:23:34,880 --> 00:23:37,974
<font color="#ffff00">If they find what they're lookin' for out
there, does that mean we get full shares?</font>

212
00:23:38,058 --> 00:23:42,312
<font color="#ffff00">Don't worry, Parker, yeah.
You'll get whatever's coming to you.</font>

213
00:23:42,396 --> 00:23:44,939
<font color="#ffff00">Look, I'm not gonna do
any more work</font>

214
00:23:45,024 --> 00:23:48,042
<font color="#ffff00">- till we get this straightened out.
- Brett,</font>

215
00:23:48,068 --> 00:23:51,654
<font color="#ffff00">you're guaranteed by law to get a share.
- What?</font>

216
00:23:51,739 --> 00:23:54,907
<font color="#ffff00">- Why don't you just fuck off.
- What?</font>

217
00:23:54,992 --> 00:23:57,410
<font color="#ffff00">What'd you say, Rip?</font>

218
00:23:57,494 --> 00:24:00,964
<font color="#ffff00">If you have any trouble,
I'll be on the bridge.</font>

219
00:24:02,583 --> 00:24:05,193
<font color="#ffff00">Hey, Ripley, come back here!</font>

220
00:24:10,257 --> 00:24:13,259
<font color="#ffff00">- Son of a bitch.
- What's the matter?</font>

221
00:24:23,270 --> 00:24:25,880
<font color="#ffff00">Can't see a god damn thing.</font>

222
00:24:26,065 --> 00:24:28,816
<font color="#ffff00">- Quit griping.
- I like griping.</font>

223
00:24:28,901 --> 00:24:30,843
<font color="#ffff00">Come on. Knock it off.</font>

224
00:25:55,028 --> 00:25:57,246
<font color="#ffff00">Ash, can you see this?</font>

225
00:25:57,330 --> 00:25:59,340
<font color="#ffff00">Yes, I can.</font>

226
00:26:02,369 --> 00:26:04,328
<font color="#ffff00">I've never seen anything like it.</font>

227
00:26:13,297 --> 00:26:15,457
<font color="#ffff00">Very bizarre.</font>

228
00:26:19,052 --> 00:26:20,795
<font color="#ffff00">You said it.</font>

229
00:26:29,772 --> 00:26:31,448
<font color="#ffff00">All right.</font>

230
00:26:32,232 --> 00:26:34,734
<font color="#ffff00">Moving on to second...
position.</font>

231
00:26:34,818 --> 00:26:36,945
<font color="#ffff00">What is it?</font>

232
00:26:39,531 --> 00:26:41,240
<font color="#ffff00">Let's get out of here.</font>

233
00:26:41,325 --> 00:26:43,993
<font color="#ffff00">We've got this far.
We must go on.</font>

234
00:26:44,077 --> 00:26:46,037
<font color="#ffff00">We have to go on.</font>

235
00:26:49,291 --> 00:26:51,560
<font color="#ffff00">Will you say that again?</font>

236
00:26:51,884 --> 00:26:53,084
<font color="#ffff00">Shit.</font>

237
00:26:54,421 --> 00:26:57,916
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Ash, as you can see,
it's kind of hard to describe.</i></font>

238
00:26:58,300 --> 00:27:00,410
<font color="#ffff00">I'm going back to the console.</font>

239
00:27:15,901 --> 00:27:18,052
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Seems to be solid.</i></font>

240
00:27:18,237 --> 00:27:20,822
<font color="#ffff00"><i>- To walk...
- You can... on it.</i></font>

241
00:27:47,766 --> 00:27:49,210
<font color="#ffff00">Dallas?</font>

242
00:28:42,404 --> 00:28:44,814
<font color="#ffff00">Come on down here.
Something different down here.</font>

243
00:28:46,074 --> 00:28:48,492
<font color="#ffff00">I don't know what it is, but...</font>

244
00:28:48,577 --> 00:28:51,954
<font color="#ffff00">See if we can get up that wall. If we
can get up that wall, we can find out.</font>

245
00:29:58,480 --> 00:30:00,081
<font color="#ffff00">Amazing.</font>

246
00:30:00,165 --> 00:30:02,633
<font color="#ffff00">Alien life-form.</font>

247
00:30:04,486 --> 00:30:07,096
<font color="#ffff00">Looks like it's been dead
a long time.</font>

248
00:30:07,280 --> 00:30:09,099
<font color="#ffff00">Fossilised.</font>

249
00:30:10,283 --> 00:30:13,069
<font color="#ffff00">Looks like it's
grown out of the chair.</font>

250
00:30:23,755 --> 00:30:25,881
<font color="#ffff00">Bones are bent outward,</font>

251
00:30:25,966 --> 00:30:28,910
<font color="#ffff00">like he exploded from inside.</font>

252
00:30:30,929 --> 00:30:33,664
<font color="#ffff00">Wonder what happened
to the rest of the crew.</font>

253
00:30:38,144 --> 00:30:40,930
<font color="#ffff00">Let's get the hell out of here.</font>

254
00:30:52,868 --> 00:30:55,969
<font color="#ffff00">Hey, Dallas, Lambert,
come on over here.</font>

255
00:30:59,124 --> 00:31:00,625
<font color="#ffff00">Come on.</font>

256
00:31:04,830 --> 00:31:08,074
<font color="#ffff00">- What do you got?
- See what you make of this.</font>

257
00:31:16,142 --> 00:31:17,660
<font color="#ffff00">Ash.</font>

258
00:31:17,684 --> 00:31:21,103
<font color="#ffff00"><i>That transmission-
Mother's deciphered part of it.</i></font>

259
00:31:21,188 --> 00:31:23,647
<font color="#ffff00">- <i>It doesn't look like an S.O.S.</i>
- What is it, then?</font>

260
00:31:23,732 --> 00:31:26,768
<font color="#ffff00">Well, I...
It looks like a warning.</font>

261
00:31:27,152 --> 00:31:29,837
<font color="#ffff00">- <i>I'm gonna go out after them.</i>
- What's the point?</font>

262
00:31:32,699 --> 00:31:35,626
<font color="#ffff00">I mean, by the time
it takes to get there, you'll...</font>

263
00:31:35,711 --> 00:31:38,270
<font color="#ffff00"><i>they'll know if it's
a warning or not, yes?</i></font>

264
00:32:05,440 --> 00:32:07,483
<font color="#ffff00">You OK down there?</font>

265
00:32:11,780 --> 00:32:14,982
<font color="#ffff00">- Can you see anything?
- Uh... a cave.</font>

266
00:32:16,034 --> 00:32:19,094
<font color="#ffff00">A ca... a cave of some sort.
But I...</font>

267
00:32:21,164 --> 00:32:24,058
<font color="#ffff00">Well, I don't know, but it's like
the god damn tropics in here.</font>

268
00:32:26,294 --> 00:32:29,021
<font color="#ffff00">What the hell is this?</font>

269
00:32:56,992 --> 00:32:59,952
<font color="#ffff00">The cave is
completely enclosed,</font>

270
00:33:00,036 --> 00:33:02,413
<font color="#ffff00">and it's full of...</font>

271
00:33:02,497 --> 00:33:06,233
<font color="#ffff00">leathery objects, like
eggs or something.</font>

272
00:33:24,144 --> 00:33:26,604
<font color="#ffff00">There's a layer of mist...</font>

273
00:33:26,688 --> 00:33:30,733
<font color="#ffff00">just covering the eggs
that reacts when broken.</font>

274
00:33:33,904 --> 00:33:35,364
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Kane?</i></font>

275
00:33:35,388 --> 00:33:36,924
<font color="#ffff00"><i>You all right?</i></font>

276
00:33:36,948 --> 00:33:39,391
<font color="#ffff00">I'm OK. All right.</font>

277
00:33:41,703 --> 00:33:43,871
<font color="#ffff00">I'm OK. I just slipped.</font>

278
00:34:04,267 --> 00:34:06,977
<font color="#ffff00">Appears to be completely sealed.</font>

279
00:34:41,830 --> 00:34:44,123
<font color="#ffff00">Wait a minute. There's movement.</font>

280
00:34:46,017 --> 00:34:49,170
<font color="#ffff00">It seems to have life. Organic life.</font>

281
00:35:54,110 --> 00:35:56,728
<font color="#ffff00">- <i>You there, Ripley?</i>
- I'm right here.</font>

282
00:36:03,203 --> 00:36:05,821
<font color="#ffff00">OK, Ripley, I'm at the
inner lock hatch now.</font>

283
00:36:05,845 --> 00:36:06,845
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Right.</i></font>

284
00:36:16,066 --> 00:36:18,817
<font color="#ffff00">- Ripley. We're clean. Let us in.
- <i>Right here.</i></font>

285
00:36:18,902 --> 00:36:21,653
<font color="#ffff00">- What happened to Kane?
- Something has attached itself to him.</font>

286
00:36:21,738 --> 00:36:24,682
<font color="#ffff00">- We have to get him to the infirmary
right away. - What kind of thing?</font>

287
00:36:24,708 --> 00:36:27,659
<font color="#ffff00">- I need a clear definition.
- An organism. Open the hatch.</font>

288
00:36:27,744 --> 00:36:30,362
<font color="#ffff00">Wait a minute. If we let it in,
the ship could be infected.</font>

289
00:36:30,446 --> 00:36:34,041
<font color="#ffff00">You know the quarantine procedure-
<i>24 hours for decontamination.</i></font>

290
00:36:34,125 --> 00:36:36,001
<font color="#ffff00">He could die in 24 hours.
Open the hatch.</font>

291
00:36:36,086 --> 00:36:38,921
<font color="#ffff00">Listen to me. If we break quarantine,
we could all die.</font>

292
00:36:39,005 --> 00:36:43,184
<font color="#ffff00">Look, would you open the god damn hatch?
We have to get him inside.</font>

293
00:36:44,761 --> 00:36:46,829
<font color="#ffff00">No. <i>I can't do that.</i></font>

294
00:36:46,913 --> 00:36:49,331
<font color="#ffff00"><i>And if you were in my position,
you'd do the same.</i></font>

295
00:36:49,416 --> 00:36:52,292
<font color="#ffff00">Ripley, this is an order. Open
that hatch right now. Do you hear me?</font>

296
00:36:52,316 --> 00:36:53,454
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Yes.</i></font>

297
00:36:53,478 --> 00:36:55,521
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Ripley, this is an order!
Do you hear me?</i></font>

298
00:36:55,605 --> 00:36:59,100
<font color="#ffff00">Yes, I read you.
The answer is negative.</font>

299
00:37:01,486 --> 00:37:03,445
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Inner hatch opened.</i></font>

300
00:37:31,266 --> 00:37:32,766
<font color="#ffff00">My God.</font>

301
00:37:43,278 --> 00:37:45,362
<font color="#ffff00">What the hell is that?</font>

302
00:37:46,656 --> 00:37:48,333
<font color="#ffff00">Jesus</font>

303
00:37:48,357 --> 00:37:49,957
<font color="#ffff00">Christ.</font>

304
00:37:51,995 --> 00:37:54,088
<font color="#ffff00">What is that, man?</font>

305
00:37:55,982 --> 00:37:58,317
<font color="#ffff00">Hey, how the hell is he breathing?</font>

306
00:37:58,501 --> 00:38:00,319
<font color="#ffff00">Is he still alive or what?</font>

307
00:38:00,403 --> 00:38:02,963
<font color="#ffff00">Why don't you guys freeze him?</font>

308
00:38:03,548 --> 00:38:05,549
<font color="#ffff00">How come they don't freeze him?</font>

309
00:38:05,633 --> 00:38:07,593
<font color="#ffff00">What's going on in there?</font>

310
00:38:07,677 --> 00:38:10,012
<font color="#ffff00">- What the fuck is going on?
- You bitch!</font>

311
00:38:10,096 --> 00:38:12,556
<font color="#ffff00">Jesus Christ! Hey! Hey!</font>

312
00:38:12,640 --> 00:38:15,492
<font color="#ffff00">- You would've left us out there.
- Break it up.</font>

313
00:38:16,176 --> 00:38:19,379
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Ripley, when I give an order,
I expect to be obeyed.</i></font>

314
00:38:19,564 --> 00:38:23,066
<font color="#ffff00">- Even if it's against the law?
- You're god damn right!</font>

315
00:38:23,151 --> 00:38:26,144
<font color="#ffff00">Maybe she has a point, you know?
Who the hell knows what that thing is.</font>

316
00:38:26,229 --> 00:38:28,722
<font color="#ffff00">How are we gonna get that off him?</font>

317
00:38:28,948 --> 00:38:32,367
<font color="#ffff00">- How are we gonna get it off?
- I'm gonna get some instruments.</font>

318
00:38:36,414 --> 00:38:37,932
<font color="#ffff00">My God.</font>

319
00:38:40,835 --> 00:38:42,088
<font color="#ffff00">Right.</font>

320
00:38:42,112 --> 00:38:44,712
<font color="#ffff00">I'll make an incision here.</font>

321
00:38:44,714 --> 00:38:48,335
<font color="#ffff00">Try and remove
one of the digitals from...</font>

322
00:38:48,359 --> 00:38:50,196
<font color="#ffff00">You're gonna do what?</font>

323
00:38:50,220 --> 00:38:53,505
<font color="#ffff00">Finger. I'm gonna try to
get his finger off. Just a minute.</font>

324
00:38:53,929 --> 00:38:55,929
<font color="#ffff00">There's one there.</font>

325
00:38:58,603 --> 00:39:02,231
<font color="#ffff00">No, that's not... it's tearing his scalp.
- I know!</font>

326
00:39:02,615 --> 00:39:06,010
<font color="#ffff00">It's not coming off
without tearing his face off with it.</font>

327
00:39:06,694 --> 00:39:08,928
<font color="#ffff00">We'll have to take a look at him inside.</font>

328
00:39:08,952 --> 00:39:09,952
<font color="#ffff00">Right.</font>

329
00:39:12,075 --> 00:39:14,526
<font color="#ffff00">How come they don't freeze him?</font>

330
00:39:14,911 --> 00:39:17,529
<font color="#ffff00"><i>How come you guys
don't freeze him?</i></font>

331
00:39:33,471 --> 00:39:35,731
<font color="#ffff00">All right,
you can take your mask off.</font>

332
00:39:54,050 --> 00:39:56,272
<font color="#ffff00">What's it got down his throat?</font>

333
00:39:56,296 --> 00:39:58,796
<font color="#ffff00">I would suggest
it's feeding him oxygen.</font>

334
00:39:59,956 --> 00:40:02,960
<font color="#ffff00">Paralyses him,
puts him in a coma,</font>

335
00:40:03,384 --> 00:40:06,620
<font color="#ffff00">then keeps him alive.
Now what the hell is that?</font>

336
00:40:07,306 --> 00:40:10,523
<font color="#ffff00">- We gotta get it off him.
- Just a minute. Just a minute.</font>

337
00:40:11,610 --> 00:40:13,869
<font color="#ffff00">I mean, let's not be too hasty.</font>

338
00:40:14,354 --> 00:40:16,622
<font color="#ffff00">We don't know anything about...</font>

339
00:40:16,806 --> 00:40:18,365
<font color="#ffff00">it.</font>

340
00:40:18,550 --> 00:40:21,760
<font color="#ffff00">Now, we're assuming it's feeding
him oxygen. If we remove it,</font>

341
00:40:23,213 --> 00:40:25,214
<font color="#ffff00">it could kill him.</font>

342
00:40:27,600 --> 00:40:30,068
<font color="#ffff00">I'm willing to take that chance.
Let's cut it off him now.</font>

343
00:40:30,094 --> 00:40:31,347
<font color="#ffff00">You'll take responsibility?</font>

344
00:40:31,371 --> 00:40:34,171
<font color="#ffff00">Yes, yes, I'll take responsibility.
Now get him out of there.</font>

345
00:40:35,658 --> 00:40:37,684
<font color="#ffff00">Where do you wanna do this?</font>

346
00:40:37,869 --> 00:40:41,038
<font color="#ffff00">We'll make an incision just
below the knuckle there.</font>

347
00:40:41,164 --> 00:40:42,889
<font color="#ffff00">- Right here.
- Stand by.</font>

348
00:40:51,591 --> 00:40:53,192
<font color="#ffff00">Good God!</font>

349
00:40:57,013 --> 00:40:59,707
<font color="#ffff00">That crap's gonna
eat through the hull.</font>

350
00:41:02,026 --> 00:41:04,719
<font color="#ffff00">That thing's gonna eat through
the god damn hull. Come on!</font>

351
00:41:04,804 --> 00:41:06,447
<font color="#ffff00">What's going on?</font>

352
00:41:07,231 --> 00:41:08,732
<font color="#ffff00">This way.</font>

353
00:41:17,367 --> 00:41:19,051
<font color="#ffff00">Next deck.</font>

354
00:41:36,760 --> 00:41:38,387
<font color="#ffff00">There it is.</font>

355
00:41:40,298 --> 00:41:42,557
<font color="#ffff00">Don't get under it!
Don't get under it.</font>

356
00:41:48,298 --> 00:41:50,299
<font color="#ffff00">Looks like it's stopping.</font>

357
00:41:53,277 --> 00:41:55,195
<font color="#ffff00">- Take a look at this, man.
- Yeah.</font>

358
00:41:55,279 --> 00:41:58,624
<font color="#ffff00">Brett, give me, uh... what do you got,
a pen there? Give it to me, quick.</font>

359
00:41:58,908 --> 00:42:00,376
<font color="#ffff00">Come on! Come on!</font>

360
00:42:05,556 --> 00:42:07,616
<font color="#ffff00">Don't get any on your arm.</font>

361
00:42:14,624 --> 00:42:16,226
<font color="#ffff00">It stopped.</font>

362
00:42:17,510 --> 00:42:19,855
<font color="#ffff00">Don't see anything like that except, uh,</font>

363
00:42:19,879 --> 00:42:21,615
<font color="#ffff00">molecular acid.</font>

364
00:42:21,639 --> 00:42:24,024
<font color="#ffff00">It must be using it for blood.</font>

365
00:42:24,809 --> 00:42:26,726
<font color="#ffff00">It's got a wonderful
defence mechanism.</font>

366
00:42:26,811 --> 00:42:29,020
<font color="#ffff00">You don't dare kill it.</font>

367
00:42:29,105 --> 00:42:30,881
<font color="#ffff00">What about Kane?</font>

368
00:42:32,742 --> 00:42:34,803
<font color="#ffff00">Here's your pen back.</font>

369
00:42:34,827 --> 00:42:36,463
<font color="#ffff00">What do we do now?</font>

370
00:42:36,487 --> 00:42:39,614
<font color="#ffff00">Leave Kane to Ash.
You get back to work.</font>

371
00:42:41,826 --> 00:42:43,643
<font color="#ffff00">Well, what...</font>

372
00:42:52,328 --> 00:42:53,563
<font color="#ffff00">OK.</font>

373
00:42:55,089 --> 00:42:56,666
<font color="#ffff00">Try it.</font>

374
00:43:01,813 --> 00:43:04,014
<font color="#ffff00">Damn it.
I thought sure that was it.</font>

375
00:43:04,140 --> 00:43:05,892
<font color="#ffff00">Try it again.</font>

376
00:43:07,477 --> 00:43:09,903
<font color="#ffff00">I feel like I've been
in this place a month.</font>

377
00:43:11,464 --> 00:43:14,149
<font color="#ffff00">We shouldn't have landed
in this place in the first place.</font>

378
00:43:15,718 --> 00:43:18,771
<font color="#ffff00">Shouldn't have landed on this damn ball,
I know that.</font>

379
00:43:20,156 --> 00:43:23,409
<font color="#ffff00">Well, the sooner we patch this
thing up and get out of here,</font>

380
00:43:23,433 --> 00:43:26,633
<font color="#ffff00">the sooner we can go home.
This place gives me the creeps.</font>

381
00:44:29,917 --> 00:44:32,361
<font color="#ffff00">That's amazing. What is it?</font>

382
00:44:34,105 --> 00:44:36,415
<font color="#ffff00">Ah, yes, it is. Um...</font>

383
00:44:37,400 --> 00:44:39,226
<font color="#ffff00">I don't know yet.</font>

384
00:44:42,921 --> 00:44:45,098
<font color="#ffff00">Did you want something?</font>

385
00:44:45,283 --> 00:44:47,376
<font color="#ffff00">Yes. I, uh...</font>

386
00:44:49,370 --> 00:44:52,289
<font color="#ffff00">I'd like to have a little talk.
How's, uh, how's Kane?</font>

387
00:44:52,373 --> 00:44:54,658
<font color="#ffff00">He's holding. No changes.</font>

