988
01:51:53,065 --> 01:51:57,051
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Final report of the commercial
starship Nostromo.</i></font>

989
01:51:57,235 --> 01:51:59,771
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Third officer reporting.</i></font>

990
01:52:00,155 --> 01:52:02,907
<font color="#ffff00"><i>The other members of the crew-</i></font>

991
01:52:03,492 --> 01:52:05,576
<font color="#ffff00">Kane, Lambert,</font>

992
01:52:05,661 --> 01:52:08,496
<font color="#ffff00">Parker, Brett,</font>

993
01:52:08,580 --> 01:52:12,392
<font color="#ffff00">Ash and Captain Dallas
are dead.</font>

994
01:52:12,876 --> 01:52:15,612
<font color="#ffff00">Cargo and ship destroyed.</font>

995
01:52:16,797 --> 01:52:20,008
<font color="#ffff00">I should reach the frontier
in about six weeks.</font>

996
01:52:20,592 --> 01:52:23,645
<font color="#ffff00">With a little luck,
the network will pick me up.</font>

997
01:52:24,429 --> 01:52:29,058
<font color="#ffff00">This is Ripley,
last survivor of the Nostromo,</font>

998
01:52:30,060 --> 01:52:32,061
<font color="#ffff00">signing off.</font>

999
01:52:38,944 --> 01:52:40,778
<font color="#ffff00">Come on, cat.</font>

